<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="fight-n">fight <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /faɪt/    美 /faɪt/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-c">1.★ <strong>[C] 战斗；打斗；[用单数] 斗争；争吵：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>win / lose a fight 
打胜/败仗</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a <strong>street fight</strong> 
街头斗殴</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a <strong>fight for</strong> freedom
争取自由的斗争</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>They <strong>had</strong> a <strong>fight with</strong> their neighbours.
他们和邻居吵了一架。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">派生词汇</h2>
<p>fighter /'faɪtə(r)/ n <br />
fighting /'faɪtɪŋ/ n   </p></div>